[{"text": "The Blue Jackal", "start": 14.25, "duration": 2.72}, {"text": "Re-written by BookBox", "start": 16.97, "duration": 5.12}, {"text": "Once upon a time", "start": 24.29, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "there was a jackal\nnamed Chandrao", "start": 25.81, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "who lived in a mighty jungle.", "start": 29.17, "duration": 2.96}, {"text": "One day,", "start": 32.13, "duration": 1.08}, {"text": "he set off in search of food", "start": 33.21, "duration": 3.12}, {"text": "and he accidentally wandered", "start": 36.33, "duration": 2.24}, {"text": "into a quiet village.", "start": 38.57, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": "When the dogs in the village", "start": 41.13, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "saw the jackal", "start": 42.45, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "they surrounded", "start": 44.65, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "and attacked him,", "start": 46.09, "duration": 1.64}, {"text": "barking away furiously.", "start": 47.73, "duration": 4.68}, {"text": "The jackal, ran for his life", "start": 52.41, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "The jackal, ran for his life", "start": 54.37, "duration": 3.48}, {"text": "and entered", "start": 57.85, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "the house of a washerman.", "start": 58.65, "duration": 3.16}, {"text": "Searching through", "start": 61.81, "duration": 0.68}, {"text": "the washerman’s house,", "start": 62.49, "duration": 2.12}, {"text": "the jackal came by", "start": 64.61, "duration": 1.92}, {"text": "a large tub", "start": 66.53, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "filled with blue dye.", "start": 68.85, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "Chandrao jumped into the tub", "start": 71.29, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": "to hide.", "start": 74.05, "duration": 2.04}, {"text": "When he left the tub,", "start": 76.09, "duration": 3.32}, {"text": "the dogs in the village", "start": 79.41, "duration": 1.64}, {"text": "did not recognize him", "start": 81.05, "duration": 2.4}, {"text": "because he was all blue!", "start": 83.45, "duration": 5.8}, {"text": "In fact,", "start": 89.25, "duration": 1.16}, {"text": "the dogs began to panic.", "start": 90.41, "duration": 7.52}, {"text": "By the afternoon,", "start": 97.93, "duration": 1.56}, {"text": "Chandrao was back\nin the jungle.", "start": 99.49, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "All the animals were confused", "start": 103.69, "duration": 3.12}, {"text": "to see such a bizarre animal.", "start": 106.81, "duration": 5.68}, {"text": "He overheard hushed\nquestions like,", "start": 112.49, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "He overheard hushed\nquestions like,", "start": 114.93, "duration": 2.72}, {"text": "“Who is this beast?”", "start": 117.65, "duration": 2.04}, {"text": "“What can it be?”", "start": 119.69, "duration": 2.64}, {"text": "Then a clever idea\nstruck him.", "start": 122.33, "duration": 7.08}, {"text": "He stood", "start": 129.41, "duration": 0.92}, {"text": "right in the middle\nof the jungle", "start": 130.33, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "and announced,", "start": 132.65, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "“My dear friends,", "start": 134.85, "duration": 1.88}, {"text": "do not fear.", "start": 136.73, "duration": 3.4}, {"text": "Brahma, the creator\nof this universe,", "start": 140.13, "duration": 3.44}, {"text": "has crafted me with his\nown hands.", "start": 143.57, "duration": 4.08}, {"text": "Lord Brahma", "start": 147.65, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "has made me the king", "start": 149.45, "duration": 2.16}, {"text": "of all three worlds ‒", "start": 151.61, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "heaven, earth, and hell.", "start": 153.13, "duration": 3.92}, {"text": "He told me to come to\nthis jungle", "start": 157.05, "duration": 3.4}, {"text": "and as there is no suitable\nking here", "start": 160.45, "duration": 3.4}, {"text": "he has asked me to be\nyour king", "start": 163.85, "duration": 3.44}, {"text": "and to protect\nall the animals.", "start": 167.29, "duration": 3.4}, {"text": "This is why I am here.", "start": 170.69, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "My friends,\nI am your caretaker.", "start": 173.89, "duration": 3.88}, {"text": "Live happily in my kingdom.”", "start": 177.77, "duration": 3.88}, {"text": "Everybody in the jungle\nbelieved him.", "start": 181.65, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "They bowed to him", "start": 185.01, "duration": 2.96}, {"text": "and said humbly,", "start": 187.97, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "“Your majesty,", "start": 191.25, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "your wish is our command.”", "start": 193.25, "duration": 3.52}, {"text": "Chandrao then chalked out", "start": 196.77, "duration": 3.16}, {"text": "everyone’s responsibilities.", "start": 199.93, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": "He made sure", "start": 201.65, "duration": 1.16}, {"text": "that most of the animals", "start": 202.81, "duration": 2.36}, {"text": "would attend to him.", "start": 205.17, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": "Clever Chandrao", "start": 207.73, "duration": 2.36}, {"text": "banished all the jackals,", "start": 210.09, "duration": 2.84}, {"text": "because he was afraid", "start": 212.93, "duration": 1.16}, {"text": "that they might\nrecognize him.", "start": 214.09, "duration": 4.8}, {"text": "The animals got busy", "start": 218.89, "duration": 1.92}, {"text": "with their responsibilities.", "start": 220.81, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": "The lion and the tiger", "start": 223.57, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "hunted", "start": 225.53, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "fresh meat", "start": 227.13, "duration": 2.04}, {"text": "for the new king.", "start": 229.17, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "Chandrao really enjoyed life\nfor some days", "start": 231.13, "duration": 1.76}, {"text": "Chandrao really enjoyed life\nfor some days", "start": 232.89, "duration": 3.6}, {"text": "until one evening,", "start": 236.49, "duration": 2.16}, {"text": "he heard the familiar", "start": 238.65, "duration": 2.8}, {"text": "“Awoo! Awoo!”", "start": 241.45, "duration": 4.16}, {"text": "cry of his fellow jackals\nfrom a distance.", "start": 245.61, "duration": 2.08}, {"text": "cry of his fellow jackals\nfrom a distance.", "start": 247.69, "duration": 2.4}, {"text": "He just could not control\nhimself.", "start": 250.09, "duration": 2.96}, {"text": "Instinctively,", "start": 253.05, "duration": 1.56}, {"text": "he too craned his neck high\nin the air", "start": 254.61, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "and let out", "start": 257.13, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "a loud “Awoo! Awoo!”", "start": 259.09, "duration": 5.36}, {"text": "When the animals heard this,", "start": 264.45, "duration": 2.64}, {"text": "they were absolutely stunned.", "start": 267.09, "duration": 4.36}, {"text": "They soon figured out what\nwas going on.", "start": 271.45, "duration": 6.2}, {"text": "Meanwhile,", "start": 277.65, "duration": 1.08}, {"text": "Chandrao realized\nhis foolishness", "start": 278.73, "duration": 3.08}, {"text": "and ran", "start": 281.81, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "for his life.", "start": 283.49, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But how could he escape", "start": 286.49, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "from so many angry animals?", "start": 289.69, "duration": 3.88}, {"text": "Well, I don’t need to", "start": 293.57, "duration": 2.28}, {"text": "describe", "start": 295.85, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "the punishment he got!", "start": 297.29, "duration": 2.88}]